1. *Podrška* je ključna u svakom projektu. (Support is key in every project.)
2. Potrebna mi je tvoja *podrška* u ovom teškom trenutku. (I need your support in this difficult moment.)
3. Naša organizacija pruža *podršku* siromašnim porodicama. (Our organization provides support to poor families.)
4. Da li imate neki oblik *podrške* za nove zaposlene? (Do you have any form of support for new employees?)
5. Molim vas da mi pružite *podršku* u ovom važnom pitanju. (Please give me your support on this important issue.)
6. Kompanija je odlučila da prekine *podršku* starim modelima računara. (The company decided to end support for old computer models.)
7. Profesorica nam pruža *podršku* tokom celog semestra. (The professor provides us with support throughout the entire semester.)
8. Moja porodica mi je uvek pružala *podršku* u svim mojim odlukama. (My family has always provided me with support in all my decisions.)
9. Uspela sam završiti projekat zahvaljujući *podršci* svojih kolega. (I managed to finish the project thanks to the support of my colleagues.)
10. Molim vas da mi pružite *podršku* u pronalaženju novog posla. (Please provide me with support in finding a new job.)